text: The material in IRM section 4.22.11 is obsolete because the study referenced is complete, and NRP is not conducting examination of C Corporation returns. If needed, prior guidance information can be found in the IRS repository. Go to http://oldirm.web.irs.gov/ for more information.
IRM 4.22.11, dated 05-24-2012 is obsolete as of the date of this transmittal.
